<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AI Engineering — Self-Study Bootcamp</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,400;9..144,600;9..144,900&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #0d0d0d;
  --bg-2: #161616;
  --bg-3: #1f1f1f;
  --bg-4: #252525;
  --ink: #f1ebe1;
  --ink-dim: #8a8378;
  --ink-faint: #4a463f;
  --accent: #d8ff3e;
  --accent-2: #ff6b35;
  --accent-3: #4ec9b0;
  --rule: #2a2a2a;
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--ink);
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}
::selection { background: var(--accent); color: var(--bg); }

.shell {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
  min-height: 100vh;
}
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .shell { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .sidebar { position: static !important; height: auto !important; }
}

.sidebar {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  height: 100vh;
  background: var(--bg-2);
  border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
  padding: 32px 24px;
  overflow-y: auto;
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 12px;
}
.sidebar-brand {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: 22px;
  line-height: 1.05;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.sidebar-brand .accent { color: var(--accent); }
.sidebar-tag {
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-dim);
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  padding-bottom: 16px;
  border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--rule);
}
.nav-week { margin-bottom: 18px; }
.nav-week-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  padding-left: 4px;
}
.nav-week a {
  display: block;
  padding: 5px 8px;
  color: var(--ink-dim);
  text-decoration: none;
  border-left: 2px solid transparent;
  transition: all 0.15s;
  line-height: 1.4;
}
.nav-week a:hover {
  color: var(--ink);
  border-left-color: var(--accent);
  background: var(--bg-3);
}
.nav-week a.active {
  color: var(--accent);
  border-left-color: var(--accent);
}
.nav-week a .day-num {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 38px;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
}
.nav-week a:hover .day-num,
.nav-week a.active .day-num { color: var(--accent); }

.main { padding: 0; max-width: 100%; overflow-x: hidden; }

.hero {
  padding: 80px 60px 100px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  position: relative;
  background: 
    radial-gradient(circle at 85% 20%, rgba(216, 255, 62, 0.06), transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 10% 80%, rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.04), transparent 50%);
}
.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: 
    linear-gradient(var(--rule) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, var(--rule) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 60px 60px;
  opacity: 0.2;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.hero-meta {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  color: var(--accent);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  position: relative;
}
.hero-meta::before { content: '●'; margin-right: 8px; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
@keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;} 50%{opacity:0.3;} }
.hero h1 {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: clamp(48px, 6.5vw, 96px);
  line-height: 0.95;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  position: relative;
}
.hero h1 .accent { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; }
.hero-sub {
  font-size: 19px;
  color: var(--ink-dim);
  max-width: 720px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  position: relative;
}
.hero-sub strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
.hero-stats { display: flex; gap: 48px; flex-wrap: wrap; position: relative; }
.stat { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
.stat-num {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: 44px;
  color: var(--accent);
  line-height: 1;
}
.stat-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-dim);
  margin-top: 6px;
}

.howto {
  padding: 60px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  background: var(--bg-2);
}
.howto-title {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.howto h2 {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 32px;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  max-width: 760px;
}
.howto-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
  gap: 20px;
}
.howto-item {
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  padding: 20px;
  background: var(--bg);
}
.howto-item-num {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--accent);
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.howto-item h3 {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 17px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.howto-item p { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.5; }

.week {
  padding: 80px 60px 40px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
}
.week-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 24px;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
  padding-bottom: 16px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.week-num {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: 88px;
  color: var(--accent);
  line-height: 0.85;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
}
.week-info { flex: 1; min-width: 280px; }
.week-tag {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.week-title {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 30px;
  line-height: 1.15;
}
.week-sub {
  color: var(--ink-dim);
  font-weight: 400;
  font-size: 17px;
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
}

.day {
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  background: var(--bg-2);
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
  scroll-margin-top: 20px;
}
.day:hover { border-color: var(--ink-faint); }
.day.open { border-color: var(--accent); }

.day-head {
  padding: 24px 28px;
  cursor: pointer;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr auto;
  gap: 24px;
  align-items: center;
  user-select: none;
}
.day-num-big {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: 38px;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  line-height: 1;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}
.day.open .day-num-big { color: var(--accent); }
.day-kicker {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.day-title {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 23px;
  line-height: 1.25;
}
.day-toggle {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--ink-dim);
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  width: 36px;
  height: 36px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  transition: all 0.2s;
}
.day.open .day-toggle {
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--bg);
  border-color: var(--accent);
}
.day-body { display: none; padding: 0 28px 32px; }
.day.open .day-body { display: block; }
.day-intro {
  padding: 24px 0 0 132px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  color: var(--ink);
  line-height: 1.7;
  border-top: 1px dashed var(--rule);
  padding-top: 24px;
  font-size: 15.5px;
}

@media (max-width: 700px) {
  .day-head { grid-template-columns: 50px 1fr auto; gap: 16px; padding: 20px; }
  .day-num-big { font-size: 28px; }
  .day-title { font-size: 17px; }
  .day-body { padding: 0 20px 24px; }
  .day-intro { padding-left: 0; }
}

.bullet {
  margin-left: 132px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  padding: 24px 0 0;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
}
.bullet:first-of-type { border-top: none; padding-top: 0; }

@media (max-width: 700px) { .bullet { margin-left: 0; } }

.bullet-header {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  align-items: baseline;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.bullet-arrow {
  color: var(--accent);
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1;
}
.bullet-heading {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 22px;
  line-height: 1.3;
  color: var(--ink);
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.bullet-explain {
  color: var(--ink);
  font-size: 15.5px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  padding-left: 30px;
}
.bullet-explain code {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 12.5px;
  background: var(--bg-3);
  padding: 1px 6px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  color: var(--accent-3);
}

.bullet-section-label {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  color: var(--accent);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin: 14px 0 10px 30px;
  padding-left: 8px;
  border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
}

.resources {
  display: grid;
  gap: 6px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  margin-left: 30px;
}
.resource {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
  gap: 14px;
  padding: 12px 16px;
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  text-decoration: none;
  color: inherit;
  transition: all 0.15s;
  background: var(--bg);
  align-items: center;
}
.resource:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateX(4px); }

.resource-type {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9.5px;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 3px 7px;
  background: var(--bg-3);
  color: var(--ink-dim);
  border-radius: 2px;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.resource-type.video { color: var(--accent-2); }
.resource-type.docs { color: var(--accent-3); }
.resource-type.course { color: var(--accent); }
.resource-type.article { color: var(--ink); }
.resource-type.code { color: #b48cff; }
.resource-type.book { color: #ff8eb8; }

.resource-info {}
.resource-title { font-weight: 500; font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.35; }
.resource-source {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10.5px;
  color: var(--ink-dim);
  margin-top: 3px;
}
.resource-arrow {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  font-size: 16px;
}
.resource:hover .resource-arrow { color: var(--accent); }

@media (max-width: 700px) {
  .bullet-explain { padding-left: 0; }
  .bullet-section-label { margin-left: 0; }
  .resources { margin-left: 0; }
  .bullet-mini { margin-left: 0 !important; }
}

.bullet-mini {
  border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-2);
  padding: 12px 16px;
  background: var(--bg);
  margin-left: 30px;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.bullet-mini-label {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent-2);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.bullet-mini p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }
.bullet-mini code {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 12px;
  background: var(--bg-3);
  padding: 1px 6px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  color: var(--accent-3);
}
.bullet-mini strong { color: var(--accent-2); }

.checkpoint {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  padding: 14px 18px;
  background: var(--bg-3);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 13px;
  margin-top: 24px;
  margin-left: 132px;
}
.checkpoint-icon { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
@media (max-width: 700px) { .checkpoint { margin-left: 0; } }

.footer {
  padding: 60px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--ink-dim);
  background: var(--bg-2);
}
.footer-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
  gap: 48px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}
@media (max-width: 700px) { .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .footer { padding: 40px 24px; } }
.footer h3 {
  font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 20px;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.footer p { margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.6; }
.footer a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
.footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
.footer-bottom {
  padding-top: 24px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 12px;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
}

.menu-toggle {
  display: none;
  position: fixed;
  top: 16px;
  right: 16px;
  z-index: 100;
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--bg);
  border: none;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  cursor: pointer;
}
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .menu-toggle { display: block; }
  .sidebar { display: none; }
  .sidebar.open { display: block; position: fixed; inset: 0; height: 100vh; z-index: 50; }
  .hero, .howto, .week { padding-left: 24px; padding-right: 24px; }
}

.day.completed .day-num-big::before {
  content: '✓';
  color: var(--accent);
  font-size: 18px;
  margin-right: 4px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<button class="menu-toggle" onclick="document.querySelector('.sidebar').classList.toggle('open')">☰ NAV</button>

<div class="shell">
  <nav class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
    <div class="sidebar-brand">AI Eng<span class="accent">/</span><br>Bootcamp</div>
    <div class="sidebar-tag">Self-Study Edition</div>

    <div class="nav-week">
      <div class="nav-week-label">Wk 1–3 · Foundations</div>
      <a href="#day-1"><span class="day-num">D01</span> Kickoff: AI Eng 2.0</a>
      <a href="#day-2"><span class="day-num">D02</span> Python & AI Stack</a>
      <a href="#day-3"><span class="day-num">D03</span> LLMs, Embeddings, VectorDBs</a>
      <a href="#day-4"><span class="day-num">D04</span> RAG, LangChain, Evals</a>
      <a href="#day-5"><span class="day-num">D05</span> Agentic AI Foundation</a>
      <a href="#day-6"><span class="day-num">D06</span> Agent Orchestration & LangGraph</a>
    </div>

    <div class="nav-week">
      <div class="nav-week-label">Wk 4–6 · Production</div>
      <a href="#day-7"><span class="day-num">D07</span> LangSmith & AWS Deployment</a>
      <a href="#day-8"><span class="day-num">D08</span> Evals & Guardrails</a>
      <a href="#day-9"><span class="day-num">D09</span> MCP</a>
      <a href="#day-10"><span class="day-num">D10</span> Context Engineering</a>
      <a href="#day-11"><span class="day-num">D11</span> Multi-Agent Systems</a>
      <a href="#day-12"><span class="day-num">D12</span> Multimodal AI</a>
    </div>

    <div class="nav-week">
      <div class="nav-week-label">Wk 7–9 · Advanced</div>
      <a href="#day-13"><span class="day-num">D13</span> Branding + Text-2-SQL</a>
      <a href="#day-14"><span class="day-num">D14</span> SLMs & Local AI</a>
      <a href="#day-15"><span class="day-num">D15</span> Deep Work + Case Study</a>
      <a href="#day-16"><span class="day-num">D16</span> Voice AI</a>
      <a href="#day-17"><span class="day-num">D17</span> Advanced AI Engineering</a>
      <a href="#day-18"><span class="day-num">D18</span> Fine-Tuning & Synthetic Data</a>
    </div>

    <div class="nav-week">
      <div class="nav-week-label">Wk 10–11 · Capstone</div>
      <a href="#day-19"><span class="day-num">D19</span> RL + AI Product Thinking</a>
      <a href="#day-20"><span class="day-num">D20</span> AI Security</a>
      <a href="#day-21"><span class="day-num">D21</span> Capstone Project</a>
      <a href="#day-22"><span class="day-num">D22</span> Interview Prep + Showcase</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="main">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-meta">22 Days · Self-Paced · Free Stack</div>
      <h1>
        AI Engineering<br>
        Bootcamp <span class="accent">Curriculum</span>,<br>
        Reverse-Engineered.
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        A self-study guide that mirrors the <strong>exact 22-day structure</strong> of a published AI Engineering bootcamp — every day's title, every sub-topic, with curated free and freemium resources mapped to each bullet. No instructor. No price tag. Just the same syllabus, made open.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">22</div><div class="stat-label">Days</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">85+</div><div class="stat-label">Sub-topics</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">200+</div><div class="stat-label">Resources</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">$0</div><div class="stat-label">Required</div></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="howto">
      <div class="howto-title">// How to use this</div>
      <h2>Each day mirrors the bootcamp's exact title and sub-bullets. Every sub-bullet has its own resources and a hands-on micro-task.</h2>
      <div class="howto-grid">
        <div class="howto-item"><div class="howto-item-num">01</div><h3>Read the explanation</h3><p>1–2 sentences on what this sub-topic actually means.</p></div>
        <div class="howto-item"><div class="howto-item-num">02</div><h3>Hit the resources</h3><p>2–3 best-in-class free links per sub-bullet. Pick one or two.</p></div>
        <div class="howto-item"><div class="howto-item-num">03</div><h3>Do the hands-on</h3><p>A small concrete task. The compounding work happens here.</p></div>
        <div class="howto-item"><div class="howto-item-num">04</div><h3>Checkpoint at end</h3><p>One question per day. Answer it before moving on.</p></div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <section class="week">
      <header class="week-header">
        <div class="week-num">01</div>
        <div class="week-info">
          <div class="week-tag">Week 1</div>
          <div class="week-title">Foundations · Setup<br><span class="week-sub">Get the dev environment, the language, and the mental model in place.</span></div>
        </div>
      </header>
      
    <article class="day" id="day-1">
      <header class="day-head">
        <div class="day-num-big">01</div>
        <div class="day-title-block">
          <div class="day-kicker">DAY 1 · WEEK 1</div>
          <div class="day-title">Kickoff: Welcome to AI Engineering 2.0</div>
        </div>
        <div class="day-toggle">+</div>
      </header>
      <div class="day-body">
        <p class="day-intro">Day one is about wiring up your environment and forming a mental map of what an AI Engineer actually does in 2026.</p>

        
      <div class="bullet">
        <div class="bullet-header">
          <span class="bullet-arrow">→</span>
          <h3 class="bullet-heading">Welcome & team introductions</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="bullet-explain">Self-study version: define why YOU are doing this. Write a one-paragraph 'why' and your target outcome (specific role, project, or skill). This becomes your anchor when motivation dips.</p>

        <div class="bullet-section-label">Resources</div>
        <div class="resources">
        <a class="resource" href="https://www.latent.space/p/ai-engineer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
