      </div>

      <div class="bullet">
        <div class="bullet-header">
          <span class="bullet-arrow">→</span>
          <h3 class="bullet-heading">RAGAS & evaluation metrics</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="bullet-explain">RAGAS scores RAG systems on faithfulness (answer grounded in context), answer relevancy, context precision, context recall. Lets you compare two RAG configs objectively.</p>

