        <span class="resource-info">
          <span class="resource-title">Evaluating agents in 2026</span>
          <span class="resource-source">LangChain Blog</span>
        </span>
        <span class="resource-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bullet-mini">
          <div class="bullet-mini-label">→ Hands-on</div>
          <p>Define 3 agent-eval metrics for your agent: (1) tool-call accuracy, (2) trajectory length, (3) task success. Score 5 traces by hand on each.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

