          <span class="bullet-arrow">→</span>
          <h3 class="bullet-heading">Sliding window management</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="bullet-explain">When chat history exceeds context, drop the oldest turns — but always keep the system prompt and recent N. Better: summarize dropped turns into one 'context so far' message.</p>

        <div class="bullet-section-label">Resources</div>
        <div class="resources">
        <a class="resource" href="https://python.langchain.com/docs/concepts/memory/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="resource-type docs">docs</span>
        <span class="resource-info">
          <span class="resource-title">LangChain Memory — sliding window types</span>
