        <div class="bullet-mini">
          <div class="bullet-mini-label">→ Hands-on</div>
          <p>Take a long system prompt (1000+ tokens). Mark it with <code>cache_control</code>. Run the same query 5 times. Compare cached vs fresh input token costs in the API response.</p>
        </div>
