      <div class="bullet">
        <div class="bullet-header">
          <span class="bullet-arrow">→</span>
          <h3 class="bullet-heading">Self-correcting SQL agents</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="bullet-explain">If the generated SQL errors out, feed the error message back to the LLM and ask for a corrected version. Loop up to 3x. Common production pattern.</p>

        <div class="bullet-section-label">Resources</div>
        <div class="resources">
        <a class="resource" href="https://langchain-ai.github.io/langgraph/tutorials/sql-agent/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="resource-type docs">docs</span>
        <span class="resource-info">
          <span class="resource-title">LangGraph SQL agent with retries</span>
          <span class="resource-source">LangGraph Docs</span>
        </span>
        <span class="resource-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
        <a class="resource" href="https://vanna.ai/blog/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
