      <div class="day-body">
        <p class="day-intro">Voice agents went from gimmicks to real products in 2024-2025. The stack: STT in, LLM middle, TTS out, glued by WebRTC for low latency.</p>

        
      <div class="bullet">
        <div class="bullet-header">
          <span class="bullet-arrow">→</span>
          <h3 class="bullet-heading">Real-time voice stack (Deepgram STT, TTS, LiveKit)</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="bullet-explain">Deepgram for streaming speech-to-text (very fast). OpenAI/ElevenLabs for text-to-speech. LiveKit for WebRTC transport. Together: full duplex voice agent.</p>

        <div class="bullet-section-label">Resources</div>
        <div class="resources">
        <a class="resource" href="https://docs.livekit.io/agents/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
