          <div class="bullet-mini-label">→ Hands-on</div>
          <p>Clone the LiveKit Python agent starter. Wire Deepgram STT → Claude → OpenAI TTS. Talk to it. Measure end-to-end latency.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bullet">
        <div class="bullet-header">
          <span class="bullet-arrow">→</span>
          <h3 class="bullet-heading">Low-latency voice systems</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="bullet-explain">Target round-trip < 800ms; > 1.5s feels broken. Stream everything: STT streams partial transcripts, LLM streams tokens, TTS streams audio chunks. No batching.</p>

        <div class="bullet-section-label">Resources</div>
