        <div class="bullet-mini">
          <div class="bullet-mini-label">→ Hands-on</div>
          <p>Profile your voice agent's latency budget: time STT, LLM, TTS separately. Identify the bottleneck. Usually it's the LLM — try a smaller model.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bullet">
        <div class="bullet-header">
          <span class="bullet-arrow">→</span>
          <h3 class="bullet-heading">Interruptions & silence handling</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="bullet-explain">When the user starts talking while the agent is speaking, stop the TTS and start listening. Detect end-of-speech with a 500-1000ms silence threshold.</p>

        <div class="bullet-section-label">Resources</div>
