        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bullet">
        <div class="bullet-header">
          <span class="bullet-arrow">→</span>
          <h3 class="bullet-heading">Semantic caching systems</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="bullet-explain">Cache by query meaning, not exact match. New query → embed → if embedding is near a cached one (cosine > 0.95), return cached answer.</p>

        <div class="bullet-section-label">Resources</div>
        <div class="resources">
        <a class="resource" href="https://gptcache.readthedocs.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
