        <div class="bullet-mini">
          <div class="bullet-mini-label">→ Hands-on</div>
          <p>Add semantic caching to your day-4 bot: store (query_embedding, answer) pairs in Chroma. Before calling the LLM, check for a near-match. Run 50 queries with 30% repeats; track hit rate.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bullet">
        <div class="bullet-header">
          <span class="bullet-arrow">→</span>
          <h3 class="bullet-heading">Smart model routing</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="bullet-explain">A small classifier decides: easy query → cheap model (Haiku, Llama 8B). Hard query → expensive model (Opus, GPT-4o). Cuts costs 60-80% with marginal quality loss.</p>

        <div class="bullet-section-label">Resources</div>
